# DataTidy23RodoSTA2005S

<!-- badges: start -->
<!-- badges: end -->

The goal of DataTidy23RodoSTA2005S is to distribute data for STA2005S regression.

## Installation

You can install the development version of DataTidy23RodoSTA2005S like so:

``` r
if (!requireNamespace("devtools")) install.packages("devtools")
devtools::install_github("TRUE/DataTidy23RodoSTA2005S")
```
